title: NetApp ONTAP: Agent Info
agents: netapp
catalog: hw/storagehw/netapp
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports errors that occurred while the NetApp ONTAP special agent
 was collecting monitoring data from the cluster.

 The service is always discovered and shows {OK} when all sections were collected
 successfully. It shows {WARN} for each section that failed to collect, displaying
 the section name and the error message. Services for affected sections will go stale.

 Sections that depend on other sections that failed to collect (e.g. {fan} and {temp}
 depend on node data) are also reported as skipped with an explanation.

discovery:
 One service is created per host monitored via the NetApp ONTAP special agent.
